{"tid":1162464,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"連登仔唔好再FF有錢就可以買俄妹做老婆","createTime":"2019-05-20T01:34:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-20T04:00:40.000Z","uid":172607,"like":4,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":8,"replies":[{"pid":"ad05b857fa91290cd914c4425689a659d5112e10","tid":1162464,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:34:58.000Z","msg":"連登仔嘅將來<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n郵購俄國新娘婚後性情大變　數學教授人財兩失：一開始就是騙局<br />\n<br />\n美國馬里蘭州（Maryland）摩根州立大學（Morgan State University）<span style=\"color: red;\">42歲數學系教授</span>法利（Jonathan Farley）為了尋找「真愛」，2013年透過一個俄羅斯「郵購新娘」<span style=\"color: red;\">網站娶得一名20歲俄國女子為妻</span>，然而婚後妻子性情大變，而且非常「大洗」，根本沒想過好好經營這段關係；<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>法利如今相信這根本是一場騙局，女方只因貪圖美國綠卡和錢才下嫁，但他已損失了約5萬美元（約40萬港元）。</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/5QwDxzn.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F5QwDxzn.png&h=a07b4453&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d65d446c2b223fe09d7fac9ac37b0d0d72481f4e","tid":1162464,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:40:38.000Z","msg":"在法利的眼中愛情也是一個統計學的問題，因為「俄羅斯的女人比男人多出1千萬人」，於是他決定前往西伯利亞（Siberia）尋找真愛。法利說：「我透過郵購新娘網站遇見她，雖然網站聲稱那是『郵購』，但從來沒有人真的用郵件方式收到新娘」。<br />\n<br />\n網站後來給法利找到一個聲稱合適的對象，雖然二人年紀相差22年，但法利仍認為值得一試，他說：「我們一直有聯絡，我寄了一封信給她，內裡約有250條問題，都是關於家庭情況、婚後要生幾個小孩等，她悉數回答。」<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qm9tUPz.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fqm9tUPz.png&h=c118f813&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n「其實我可以對你更狠心」<br />\n<br />\n隨後二人陷入熱戀，法利甚且見過對方家長，3年後二人在美國陶森法院（Towson courthouse）結婚。法利當時以為這是幸福的開始，沒想到婚後僅兩個星期，老婆的態度竟180度大轉變，「我們不停吵架，而且她非常『大洗』，例如我們去Walmart她也可以花400美元（約3100港元），去Bed Bath &amp; Beyond她花900美元（約7100港元），我甚至不記得在Ikea花了多少錢。」<br />\n<br />\n直到某日，老婆稱想要買一件新外套，法利表示一起去買，沒想到老婆竟大發雷霆，怒吼「把錢給我就好，就500美元（約3900港元）」，此刻法利終驚覺不妥，並萌生離婚念頭。<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/3n1j1uG.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F3n1j1uG.png&h=282b1bf8&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n法利之後仍曾嘗試與老婆和解，但二人又再次為錢吵架，老婆甚至在餐廳當眾把紅酒往他臉上潑去，法利才下定決心簽署分居協議書，用3000美元（約23500港元）買機票送女方去土耳其，惟在駕車去機場途中，女方竟說「其實我可以對你更狠心」。法利稱：「當時我不明白她所指的是甚麼，我不認為她可以做得更狠，因為我的信用卡已經一度欠款1.2萬美元（約9.4萬港元）。」<br />\n<br />\n家中搬剩一張枱三張櫈<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: large;\">法利回到家後卻發現，家中只剩下一張枱和三張櫈，其餘東西都被女方於兩日內搬走了。法利說：「那時我才明白她那些奇怪的行為，從一開始這就是一場騙局，她只是為了得到綠卡和花光我的錢，她從沒有打算經營這段婚姻」。</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n法利選擇報警求助，但由於二人只是處於分居狀態，法律上仍是夫婦，故此當局亦無能為力。<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>法利希望當局能修改法例，以保護婚姻詐騙的受害人，又強調自己不會再上那些約會網站，將更加專注研究數學，「縱使我教了這麼多年的書，但不得不承認，那樣的詐騙手法很高明。」</strong></span></span><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/hkOixBr.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FhkOixBr.png&h=ec7cb018&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/sCHbSBs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FsCHbSBs.png&h=0025b973&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"a974c460627a5c1849a0b535d81005ba248bea50","tid":1162464,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T01:41:45.000Z","msg":"42歲毒撚想娶個20歲嘅下場就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0fd00f0539a083a4d491e3f96c96eefd0d299b32","tid":1162464,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:09:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"794547def82a65f95127718f197fc08ebcc6982c","tid":1162464,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:10:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e625881cc0882fff2b5b57ca5ca275a26b81c708","tid":1162464,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:15:41.000Z","msg":"我間劏房連一張枱三張櫈都放唔落，好放心"},{"pid":"5cfd00ba686ac75658b688d14b22629b271dcb44","tid":1162464,"uid":161935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:20:03.000Z","msg":"個騙徒就蒙面，受害者就出樣。"},{"pid":"77cdd6ff361c37be1e4b156b36404a5f4d25d030","tid":1162464,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5cfd00ba686ac75658b688d14b22629b271dcb44","tid":1162464,"uid":161935,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:20:03.000Z","msg":"個騙徒就蒙面，受害者就出樣。"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:49:47.000Z","msg":"傳媒就係咁<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4787f30361fc135b269d5354b4624920148e5d8","tid":1162464,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"e625881cc0882fff2b5b57ca5ca275a26b81c708","tid":1162464,"uid":34409,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:15:41.000Z","msg":"我間劏房連一張枱三張櫈都放唔落，好放心"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:50:10.000Z","msg":"杜絕呢d女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"79bd9db5dd322820faa0ebeecddfdd11643d549b","tid":1162464,"uid":172607,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:51:47.000Z","msg":"身邊真係聽到有差唔多40歲嘅男同事話打算同大陸妹結婚<br />\n我真係笑而不語<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n為左有西屌 係香港都無港女要 就退而求其次搵大陸女人<br />\n甘願比佢地搵笨<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6dbd297baa564d581f62b8fce9ad180733110b91","tid":1162464,"uid":104804,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:52:13.000Z","msg":"同大陸妹結婚一樣？"},{"pid":"0b1a7c2ce0fd4906ea7c1f91e01948bfb4888b4c","tid":1162464,"uid":183567,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:52:55.000Z","msg":"數學教授......"},{"pid":"c84311ac1021b50010e371f1fdb589e5b8b7a91e","tid":1162464,"uid":19126,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:56:08.000Z","msg":"其實數學人係咪太理性，感覺雙方都係好理性，各取所需<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n一開波就問250條問題根本已經痴撚線<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f1486d0034ce41d709078c489ac8db30e6fa6d6b","tid":1162464,"uid":117509,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:57:18.000Z","msg":"仲要係尼架<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e3715e3f9c347d91168f0597c60e5483e69dffb","tid":1162464,"uid":29080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:58:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e93bc6210f14c2f0b182691180d2bf6304901244","tid":1162464,"uid":172607,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c84311ac1021b50010e371f1fdb589e5b8b7a91e","tid":1162464,"uid":19126,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-05-20T02:56:08.000Z","msg":"其實數學人係咪太理性，感覺雙方都係好理性，各取所需<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\